items.question: Which programming language has the most projects?
items.sql:
SELECT
  repos.repository_language,
  ((names.total / repos.total) * 100) per,
FROM (
  SELECT
  repository_language,
  COUNT(UNIQUE(repository_name)) total
  FROM 
    [githubarchive:github.timeline]
  WHERE
    type = 'PushEvent'
  AND
    repository_language IS NOT NULL
  GROUP BY
    repository_language) names
JOIN (
  SELECT
    repository_language,
    COUNT(*) total
  FROM (
    SELECT
      repository_language,
    FROM
      [githubarchive:github.timeline]
    WHERE
      repository_language IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY
      repository_language,
      repository_name)
  GROUP BY
    repository_language
  HAVING
    total > 4000) repos
ON
  repos.repository_language = names.repository_language
ORDER BY
  per DESC
LIMIT 10
items.inputSQL:

FROM (

  COUNT(UNIQUE(repository_name)) total
  FROM 
    [githubarchive:github.timeline]
  WHERE
    type = 'PushEvent'
  AND
    repository_language IS NOT NULL
  GROUP BY
    repository_language) names
JOIN (
  SELECT
    repository_language,
    COUNT(*) total
  FROM (
    SELECT
      repository_language,
    FROM
      [githubarchive:github.timeline]
    WHERE
      repository_language IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY
      repository_language,
      repository_name)
  GROUP BY
    repository_language
  HAVING
    total > 4000) repos
ON
  repos.repository_language = names.repository_language
WHERE
  lower(names.repository_language) = lower('userInput')
ORDER BY
  per DESC
LIMIT 10

items.question: Which football team had the most popular page in the past month?
items.sql:
SELECT
  topic_wiki.name AS name,
  SUM(requests) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    topic.mid AS mid,
    topic.name AS name,
    REPLACE(REPLACE(wiki.title, '$0028', '('), '$0029', ')') AS title
  FROM (
    SELECT
      mid,
      name
    FROM
      [freebase_tags.football_teams]) topic
  JOIN (
    SELECT
      REGEXP_REPLACE(REGEXP_REPLACE(obj, '/wikipedia/en/', ''), '/wikipedia/id/', '') AS title,
      sub AS mid
    FROM
      [fh-bigquery:freebase20140119.triples_nolang]
    WHERE
      obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/en'
      OR obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/id'
      AND pred = '/type/object/key') wiki
  ON
    wiki.mid = topic.mid) topic_wiki
JOIN
  [fh-bigquery:wikipedia.pagecounts_201604] views
ON
  views.title = topic_wiki.title
GROUP BY
  mid,
  name
ORDER BY
  total DESC
LIMIT
  10
IGNORE CASE

items.question: Which superhero was mentioned the most in /r/movies in the past month?
items.sql:
SELECT
  pop_topic.name,
  COUNT(UNIQUE(comments.id)) AS total
FROM (
  SELECT
    topic_wiki.mid AS mid,
    topic_wiki.name AS name,
    SUM(requests) AS total
  FROM (
    SELECT
      topic.mid AS mid,
      topic.name as name,
      REPLACE(REPLACE(wiki.title, '$0028', '('), '$0029', ')') AS title
    FROM (
      SELECT
        mid,
        name
      FROM
        [freebase_tags.superheroes]) topic
    JOIN (
      SELECT
        REGEXP_REPLACE(REGEXP_REPLACE(obj, '/wikipedia/en/', ''), '/wikipedia/id/', '') AS title,
        sub AS mid
      FROM
        [fh-bigquery:freebase20140119.triples_nolang]
      WHERE
        obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/en'
        OR obj CONTAINS '/wikipedia/id'
        AND pred = '/type/object/key') wiki
    ON
      wiki.mid = topic.mid) topic_wiki
  JOIN
    [fh-bigquery:wikipedia.pagecounts_201604] views
  ON
    views.title = topic_wiki.title
  GROUP BY
    mid,
    name
  ORDER BY
    total DESC
  LIMIT
    100 ) pop_topic
CROSS JOIN (
  SELECT
    id,
    body
  FROM
    [fh-bigquery:reddit_comments.2016_03]
  WHERE
    subreddit = 'movies') comments
WHERE
  comments.body CONTAINS CONCAT(' ', pop_topic.name, ' ')
GROUP BY
  pop_topic.name,
ORDER BY
  total DESC
IGNORE CASE
